## In a paragraph or more, outline your next steps. What new skills will you need to acquire? What topics will you need to research? If your working with one or two classmates,
who will do what?
I will need to acquire new skills in game development, Python programming, and Pygame library. Specifically, I will need to learn how to implement game mechanics such 
as collision detection, pathfinding algorithms, and scoring systems. I will also need to research how to design and draw mazes using Pygame, as well as how to 
incorporate audio and visual effects into the game. Additionally, I may need to learn how to optimize the game's performance and memory usage to ensure smooth gameplay.

